'''牛津大學聖史蒂芬院'''（'''St Stephen’s House, Oxford'''。當地稱：Staggers）是[[牛津大學|牛津大學]]的一所[[永久私人學堂|永久私人學堂]]，由[[英國國教|英國國教]]管理，教授[[神學|神學]]。此院由[[牛津運動|牛津運動]]的成員成立于1876年<ref>[https://www.ssho.ox.ac.uk/about/history.html "History"] {{Wayback|url=https://www.ssho.ox.ac.uk/about/history.html |date=20200910035717 }}, St Stephen's House official website. Accessed 8 April 2014.</ref>，主要創始人是後來的[[林肯主教|林肯主教]]、當時的牛津大學神學教授（Regius Professor of Pastoral Theology）愛德華·金（Edward King）<ref>[http://books.google.co.uk/books?id=OfFmAAAAMAAJ&dq=bishop+edward+king&focus=searchwithinvolume&q=st+stephen Berkeley William Randolph & R. W. Townroe, ''The Mind and Work of Bishop King'' (A. R. Mowbray, 1919), p. 88] {{Wayback|url=http://books.google.co.uk/books?id=OfFmAAAAMAAJ&dq=bishop+edward+king&focus=searchwithinvolume&q=st+stephen |date=20140408212827 }}. Accessed 8 April 2014.</ref>。
